Jherruk budhun iyâ arèya tombuwân sè tamaso' ka ḍâlem famili Rutaceae. Tombuwân arèya èkoca' kèya ''bitter orange, sour orange'' (Inggris); ''limau samar'' (Malaysia); ''cabuso, cabiso'' (Filipina); bân èn-laènna<ref>https://uses.plantnet-project.org/en/Citrus_aurantium_(PROSEA)</ref>. Èparkèra'aghi jherruk budhun arèya ''hibrida'' ḍâri [[jherruk macan]] bân [[jherruk mandarin]]<ref>https://pfaf.org/user/Plant.aspx?LatinName=Citrus+aurantium</ref>.
